com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F1794992154&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d981cc3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/1794992154</a><br />\n<br />\n滑捋捋、滑脟脟都見過，唔知邊個啱"},{"pid":"3ce06ae6891230d25baebb0b5eb035a28fd41d5a","tid":186201,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>La字原來已有<br />\n𢲡住痛<br />\n好𢲡痛</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似係揦"},{"pid":"f66bcd24d1c27df08b7adf88ad78fa6b5f7f361d","tid":186201,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"齊輯輯?"},{"pid":"24a58e17cdeb018e4133c1137737591a8423762b","tid":186201,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hea字係寫「休」<br />\n利申大學中文堂教嘅</blockquote><br />\n我估格硬搵返個近義黎代入個音度既姐<br />\n好多依類字個音應該本身係語音上自然演化出黎<br />\n唔係本身有個字再讀歪組合生成</blockquote><br />\n古代個休字前面帶h音，其實古音可能同hea字相似<br />\n讀音唔會無中生有，通常可以對應返一個字，不過讀音會不斷演變，到最後可能同個字match唔返</blockquote><br />\n我唔係指無中生有<br />\n已存在既粵語每個音每個調都已經附帶特定情感意思，比如改英文名時望住英文字母組合，唔會附帶意思，但讀音你大腦會自動聯想到特定感覺，比如同咩中文字音相似佢地又係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n所以我認同新字絕對因應舊字發展出黎，但我覺得好多新字唔係由另一個字演變出黎，而係所有字同時作用下比到某個字音或詞結合起黎既音有適合表達某種感覺既獨特性，而大家容易接受而流傳開去<br />\n其實好合理，否則古代邊得咁多古字黎演變出新字，佢地創到無字借咪迫住創字<br />\n類似係 top down bottom up兩種方向演變<br />\n粵語咪好多詞，頭一個字形容詞，第二三字疊字，滑saisai, 滑lulu, 滑dudu, 黃gumgum....依類詞我相信有好多先音後借古字情況<br />\n<br />\nPs 非語言學家 純自己諗</blockquote><br />\n不過hea字似乎唔係咁，因為讀音同意思都同休相似，應該係直接讀音變化演變出嚟</blockquote><br />\n巴打冇聽書啦<br />\n佢係教 HEA 係休<br />\n不過係客家定唔知潮洲話<br />\n可能係以前香港D 細路學一半唔學一半<br />\n貪得意就用黎講自己冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老師話想同你講聲「真乖」，有聽書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我一路覺得，&quot;HEA&quot;係打錯字，真正係打&quot;HAE&quot;<br />\n用例子比較一下︰<br />\nSea(海洋) = 讀作 Cee~~<br />\nTea(茶) = 讀作 Teee~~<br />\nPea(豌豆) = 讀作 Peee~~~<br />\n如果有個詞語叫&quot;Hea&quot;，根據英文發音習慣，一定讀作 &quot;Hee~~~&quot;，唔會係&quot;Hair&quot;<br />\n<br />\n可能咁講好似好怪，但我覺得係打&quot;Hae&quot; / &quot;H&aelig;&quot;"},{"pid":"0e469a347f94673b9ff6bd85ad4c39e63e1c54dc","tid":186201,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"師師縮縮"},{"pid":"dfec84e7c77a6b76e3d1b5e58b6f13fee310eca0","tid":186201,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Dum垃圾<br />\n求字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n揼</blockquote><br />\n長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係抌</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndump係英文嚟<br />\n<br />\n好多時所謂正字，特別係彭志銘嗰D，都係穿鑿附會，張冠李戴"},{"pid":"063e13e24480a2b11eb3ad2587711ede49ced0a9","tid":186201,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"把刀寒住條頸個寒"},{"pid":"7479e0956bb046ad37b150606fdcb4a9059d771b","tid":186201,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"Chic褲<br />\n休褲"},{"pid":"f1713fcaa0867e22200031a0d6f78d2e4bcf2346","tid":186201,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chic褲<br />\n休褲</blockquote><br />\n蹙？"},{"pid":"e7a774e292443c7ccbdd38606a62bbd2dc51a4d1","tid":186201,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"淋「支支」「bet bet」<br />\n瞓得好「lum」<br />\n隊「lum」<br />\n白「sai sai」<br />\n蛇「guea」<br />\n滑「劣劣」<br />\nou4勻 (shake到均勻)<br />\n青「bb」<br />\n軟「lai lai」"},{"pid":"2727b09422bf8065fa876d5ebc8200b19f7d6bdd","tid":186201,"uid":74229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20